item.title: Can somone please help me find this program..... :)
item.dc:creator: @jme jme
item.description:
@jme wrote:

Im not kidding, it's known that realmcrafter has not been cracked yet. I bought the program, and it can only run on one computer or it stops working too. I'd explain the auth system but there are no cracks or illegal versions of it out yet, only fake ones that dont work. Many crackers have givin up on it(I used to skim through a crack forum before and they quit on it, mainly because it's updated so much)

It's great for the content that it comes with, I now have like 5000 amazing textures, and a few 3d models. Either way it's a powerful tool but cannot do like 80% of the stuff it says it can do. I am on the forums for quite a bit, you'll notice from the screenshots that we stole the terrain pics and terrain heightmaps It was great when this thing came out because before it we had no 3d models to put into our game, and then we were able to put tonnes of placeholders that this program comes with.
